{"tid":1155211,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［無圖］生命結束前 應該做的事","createTime":"2019-05-14T20:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T00:38:12.000Z","uid":65395,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1476a197814eeb9053607a1b897d43a38895e0cd","tid":1155211,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"如果一個人即將會離開人世<br />\n應該爲乜野人做乜野事？<br />\n自身？家人？朋友？社會？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自身；用曬全部錢 全部身家 吃喝玩樂 買 <br />\n<br />\n家人：用正規方法搵大量錢 ，買最好既物資比家人 及 留錢比佢地<br />\n<br />\n朋友：無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會：用正規方式 幫助有需要既人 ，千奇唔好報復社會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地又會點揀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 良好市民 ，本地年青人，無公屋無車無朋友無希望 月入萬三  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eea1192f32d715bb2ab40a937d3848b9c710cf1","tid":1155211,"uid":93136,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:22:15.000Z","msg":"我係你朋友<br />\n可以比少少我"},{"pid":"a9083bf5cdf124fab32d38c944b5529cbc9fe679","tid":1155211,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eea1192f32d715bb2ab40a937d3848b9c710cf1","tid":1155211,"uid":93136,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:22:15.000Z","msg":"我係你朋友<br />\n可以比少少我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:25:34.000Z","msg":"好 無問題啦朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你戶口係？"},{"pid":"b9a675dd30680fb31f50a10174046a03946019fe","tid":1155211,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS7bgHNL6m04o96LIMtUhPZTlGyPjH6BtJDXb_bopiRXJDx93M_\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcS7bgHNL6m04o96LIMtUhPZTlGyPjH6BtJDXb_bopiRXJDx93M_&h=90153488&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b22f1279c5769b3a430adf75e39e0029aa0ab6ed","tid":1155211,"uid":65395,"like":0